Package: RInno
Type: Package
Title: Deploy Local Shiny Apps Using Inno Setup
Version: 0.0.0.9001
Author: person('Jonathan', 'Hill', email = 'hill@ficonsulting.com', role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Jonathan M. Hill <hill@ficonsulting.com>
URL: www.ficonsulting.com
Description: This package helps introduce Inno Setup to R users. Inno Setup is an open source software project, which is focused on building installers for Windows with a complete feature set to manage software deployments. It can be used to deploy local Shiny applications, reports or R scripts like any other software with a setup wizard.
